CITY OF HOLLY HILL, a municipal corporation under and by virtue of the laws of the State of Florida, v. MILLARD B. CONKLIN. 22 So. (2nd) 816

June Term, 1945

July 17, 1945 Division B Horn & OssinsTty and Harry A. Horn, for petitioner. W. W. Judge and Millard B. Conklin, for respondent. PER CURIAM:

Petition for certiorari denied.

CHAPMAN, C. J., BROWN, THOMAS and SEBRING, JJ., concur.
